data.description: Welcome to this stunning 5 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom residence in the Alamo Ranch area on the far west side of San Antonio. This home greets you with exceptional curb appeal, a welcoming front porch, and two mature trees that provide a shade canopy. Inside, discover a flexible space at the entrance, perfect for a formal dining or living area, leading to a spacious kitchen and living area. The kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring an island, stainless steel appliances, and pristine white cabinetry. The living area boasts a lofty ceiling, enhancing the sense of space. The primary bedroom serves as a peaceful retreat with an en-suite bathroom, while the additional rooms offer generous space for rest. Upstairs, a loft area adds extra versatility. Outside, the backyard is a dream with a covered patio and wooden deck extension, offering privacy with no direct neighbors behind. This gorgeous home combines modern comfort with functionality, making it an ideal sanctuary for those seeking a serene living experience.  Seller has a current VA assumable rate below 3%
